These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 8

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-1::.
There 4 different types of food: potato, kale, strawberry, pear
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: biathlon, rowing, rugby, tennis
1. the person eating strawberry is between the person who's sport is rugby and the person who's sport is rowing##2
2. the person eating pear is on the left or right of the person who's sport is rugby##3
3. the person who's sport is rugby is not to the left of the person who's sport is rugby##8
4. the person who's sport is rowing is not the person eating strawberry##6
5. the person eating strawberry is somewhere to the right of the person eating potato##5
6. the person eating potato is on the right of the person who's sport is biathlon##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1     |    2    |    3    |   4    |
| Food   | pear  | potato | strawberry | kale  |
| Sport   | biathlon | rugby   | tennis  | rowing |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-2::.
The people use 4 different means of transport: skateboard, helicopter, subway, airplane
The people have 4 different jobs:  designer, journalist, nurse, project-manager
1. the project-manager is not to the left of the project-manager##8
2. the person driving the skateboard is somewhere to the right of the person driving the airplane##5
3. the person driving the skateboard is the journalist##1
4. the person driving the airplane is between the person driving the skateboard and the person driving the helicopter##2
5. the person driving the helicopter is somewhere between the person driving the subway and the designer##7
6. the nurse is somewhere to the left of the person driving the helicopter##5
7. the designer is not to the left of the designer##8

.:: Answer ::.
|        |     1      |        2        |    3     |     4      |
| Transport   | subway | helicopter          | airplane | skateboard     |
| Job    | nurse      | project-manager | designer | journalist |

