.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-3::.
There 4 different types of food: cucumber, eggplant, lime, lettuce
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: adventure, comedy, family, superhero
1. the person watching adventure movies is not to the left of the person eating lime##8
2. the person watching comedy movies is on the far left##1
3. the person eating eggplant is on the right of the person eating cucumber##1
4. the person eating eggplant is in an even position##4
5. the person eating lettuce is on the far left or far right##3
6. the person eating cucumber is somewhere to the left of the person watching superhero movies##5
7. the person eating lettuce is the person watching family movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |     3     |     4     |
| Food           | cucumber | eggplant | lime     | lettuce |
| Movie-Genre   | comedy    | superhero   | adventure | family    |

