.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-4::.
There 4 different types of food: orange, pineapple, spinach, peas
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: lacrosse, parkour, soccer, weightlifting
1. the person who's sport is parkour is on the left of the person who's sport is weightlifting##1
2. the person who's sport is lacrosse is not to the left of the person who's sport is parkour##8
3. the person who's sport is soccer is on the right of the person eating pineapple##1
4. the person eating peas is not to the right of the person who's sport is soccer##8
5. the person eating orange is the person who's sport is lacrosse##1
6. the person eating orange is on the right of the person who's sport is soccer##1
7. the person eating spinach is somewhere to the left of the person eating peas##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |       2       |   3    |    4     |
| Food   | spinach   | pineapple         | peas   | orange    |
| Sport         | parkour | weightlifting | soccer | lacrosse |

