2. the german is somewhere to the left of the person eating cauliflower##5
3. the person eating lettuce is on the right of the spanish##1
4. the polish is on the left or right of the spanish##3
5. the person eating cauliflower is somewhere to the left of the person eating kiwi##5
6. the person eating pineapple is not to the left of the german##8
7. the person eating pineapple is the german##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |   3   |    4    |
| Food          | pineapple | cauliflower | kiwi  | lettuce |
| Nationality   | german   | french         | spanish | polish |

