The people prefer 4 different types of sport: baseball, ice-hockey, rugby, tennis
1. the colonial house is not to the right of the person who's sport is tennis##8
2. the person who's sport is tennis is somewhere to the right of the person who's sport is rugby##5
3. the townhouse house is on the left of the person who's sport is rugby##1
4. the person who's sport is rugby is somewhere between the person who's sport is ice-hockey and the townhouse house##7
5. the colonial house is not to the right of the tower house##8
6. the tower house is somewhere between the person who's sport is ice-hockey and the colonial house##7

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1      |      2       |        3        |     4      |
| House     | townhouse | colonial | tower | ranch-style     |
| Sport   | baseball   | rugby        | tennis          | ice-hockey |

