.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-9::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: classical, dubstep, indie, pop
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: february, october, july, december
1. the fan of classical is between the fan of pop and the person who's birthday is in february##2
2. the person who's birthday is in december is on the far left##1
3. the person who's birthday is in december is on the left or right of the fan of classical##3
4. the fan of dubstep is somewhere to the right of the person who's birthday is in february##5
5. the person who's birthday is in october is the person who's birthday is in october##1
6. the fan of indie is not the person who's birthday is in july##6
7. the fan of pop is not to the right of the fan of indie##8
8. the person who's birthday is in february is not to the left of the person who's birthday is in october##8

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |     2     |   3   |    4    |
| Music-Genre   | pop   | classical | indie | dubstep |
| Birthday     | december | october       | february  | july    |

