2. the owner of the rabbit is not the librarian##6
3. the owner of the rabbit is on the right of the chef##1
4. the manager is not to the right of the chef##8
5. the owner of the rabbit is on the left or right of the chef##3
6. the owner of the rat is not to the right of the owner of the rabbit##8

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1    |     2     |    3     |     4      |
| Job         | manager | chef      | writer   | librarian  |
| Pet   | horse    | rat | rabbit | turtle |

