.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-13::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: cola, fanta, juice, soy-milk
The people have 4 different hobbies: fishing, reading, filmmaking, card-games
1. the person who's hobby is card-games is not to the right of the person who's hobby is fishing##8
2. the person who's hobby is card-games is not to the right of the person drinking cola##8
3. the person who's hobby is reading is on the left of the person drinking fanta##1
4. the person drinking cola is on the far left or far right##3
5. the person drinking soy-milk is on the far left or far right##3
6. the person who's hobby is fishing is somewhere between the person who's hobby is filmmaking and the person drinking fanta##7
7. the person who's hobby is fishing is on the left or right of the person drinking fanta##3
8. the person drinking soy-milk is on the left or right of the person drinking fanta##3

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |       2       |    3     |     4      |
| Beverage   | soy-milk | fanta         | juice    | cola       |
| Hobby      | reading | card-games | fishing | filmmaking |

