4. the person drinking almond-milk is between the person drinking tea and the paramedic##2
5. the person drinking 7up is on the far left##1
6. the fisherman is between the security-guard and the freelancer##2

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1    |      2      |     3      |      4       |
