2. the person who's sport is rowing is not to the right of the owner of the rabbit##8
3. the owner of the fish is somewhere between the owner of the rabbit and the owner of the snake##7
4. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is somewhere to the right of the owner of the cat##5
5. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is somewhere to the left of the person who's sport is lacrosse##5
6. the person who's sport is rugby is not to the right of the person who's sport is ice-hockey##8
7. the owner of the fish is not to the left of the person who's sport is lacrosse##8

.:: Answer ::.
|             |  1   |   2   |   3   |    4    |
| Pet         | cat  | snake | fish  | rabbit  |
| Sport   | rugby | ice-hockey   | lacrosse | rowing |

